sentences: Daniel Douglas Orlando (born May 29, 1981), also known as Funkefeller, is an Electro House producer from Phoenix, Arizona.
Daniel Douglas Orlando began his music career at the age of 4 years old.
His father, Douglas Orlando, gave him piano lessons for many years.
Nonetheless, Orlando enjoyed most of his days growing up playing in his father's music studio.
